DEPENDENCIES
----------------------------------------------------------------
Java and Javac must be version 1.7 or above.

Java libraries:
* Selenium client and webdriver bindings
	- http://docs.seleniumhq.org/download/ (You want the Java Client & WebDriver language bindings, obviously)

* args4j
	- http://args4j.kohsuke.org/

* Jetty
	- Ships bundled with Eclipse (suggested option) http://www.eclipse.org/

* JDBC driver 
	- http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/sqlserver/aa937724(v=msdn.10).aspx
	
* Freemarker templating engine 
	- http://freemarker.org/
	
* JavaMail 
	- http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javamail/index.html


